id: 93
event: agent
data: {"type":"text_delta","delta":"The brand system is dark, fire-led, and editorial: black-brown grounds, ivory logo work, lamb/fire/seafood as the narrative, with refined but theatrical copy. I’m using a multi-page rhythm: home as the cinematic overview, menu as a dense editorial menu index, functions as private dining, and contact as the practical close."}

: keepalive

